{"word":"παροράω","slug":"παροράω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παροράω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-όψομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>παρεῖδον</el>) (aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-ώφθην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>-ῶμμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to look at by the way, notice, remark</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τί τινι</el> something in one, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to overlook, disregard, neglect</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to see amiss, see wrong</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>IV. </b><i>to look sideways</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}